    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require all workplaces to pay employees every fortnight",
        "additional_details": "I think that if this was put in place, people would have faith that their concerns are being addressed.",
        "background": "I want the government to consider the cost of living and require workplaces to pay their employees every two weeks. I think this could help manage debts and other expenses and reduce the the mental and financial burden on citizens.",
